@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<style>
    .about-container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .about-header {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #39a554;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .about-section-title {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: #343a40;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .about-text {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: #555;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .about-list {
        padding-left: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .about-list li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .about-icon {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: #39a554;
        margin-right: 0.5rem;
    }

    .text-center-strong {
        text-align: center;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #343a40;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }
</style>

<div class="about-container">
    <h2 class="about-header">About Our Platform</h2>

    <p class="about-text">
        Welcome to our nutritional information platform, where we aim to help companies evaluate their food products' eligibility for the <strong>Nøkkelhull</strong> symbol – a trusted indicator of healthier food choices.
        By providing an easy way for companies to input detailed nutritional data, we ensure they can quickly assess if their products meet the specific nutritional criteria set for "Nøkkelhull" certification.
    </p>

    <h4 class="about-section-title"><i class="about-icon fas fa-info-circle"></i>What is the Nøkkelhull Symbol?</h4>
    <p class="about-text">
        The <strong>Nøkkelhull</strong> symbol, widely recognized across Scandinavia, signifies a commitment to healthier nutrition. Products with this label meet standards in categories such as reduced energy (calories), lower fat, adequate protein, balanced carbohydrates, and minimized salt content. 
        By achieving this label, companies signal their dedication to providing healthier options, and consumers gain a reliable way to make smarter choices when shopping.
    </p>

    <h4 class="about-section-title"><i class="about-icon fas fa-bullseye"></i>Our Mission</h4>
    <p class="about-text">
        Our mission is twofold:
    </p>
    <ul class="about-list">
        <li><strong>For Companies:</strong> We provide a streamlined tool for companies to enter and review their food products' nutritional values, helping them assess if they qualify for the Nøkkelhull label.</li>
        <li><strong>For Consumers:</strong> We offer a comprehensive resource for people to explore nutritional details of products, supporting healthier choices.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4 class="about-section-title"><i class="about-icon fas fa-tasks"></i>How It Works</h4>
    <p class="about-text">
        Companies can use our platform to:
    </p>
    <ol class="about-list">
        <li><strong>Add new food products</strong> with complete nutritional information.</li>
        <li><strong>Evaluate eligibility</strong> for the Nøkkelhull label based on provided criteria.</li>
        <li><strong>Update and manage</strong> product information to stay aligned with nutritional standards.</li>
    </ol>

    <p class="about-text">
        Consumers can browse our website to:
    </p>
    <ol class="about-list">
        <li><strong>Search for products</strong> they wish to learn more about.</li>
        <li><strong>Check nutritional details</strong> like calories, fat, protein, carbohydrates, and salt content to make informed decisions.</li>
    </ol>

    <h4 class="about-section-title"><i class="about-icon fas fa-shield-alt"></i>Our Commitment to Transparency</h4>
    <p class="about-text">
        We believe in the importance of transparency in food nutrition. By allowing companies to share their nutritional information and helping consumers access it freely, we aim to foster a community focused on better health and well-being.
    </p>

    <p class="text-center-strong">Let’s build a healthier future, one product at a time.</p>
</div>


